        <tr>
            <td width="100%">
            <div id="customerLogo"><img alt="" border="0" src="cid:riLCSt1J4a"></div>
            <div style="font: 12px verdana" id="messagebody">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="font: 12px verdana" id="Signature"><br>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 36.75pt; text-indent: -18.75pt"><font face="Calibri"><strong><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: red">1.</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: red">SAP Trainer -</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 22pt">MM, SD and WM </span></strong></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Contract Position: 6 months</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">St Louis, MO</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font face="Calibri"><span style="background: yellow">May need to interview on site &ndash; we do not pay for travel costs.</span> </font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font face="Calibri">Training - SAP MM, SD and WM modules in customer service, demand planning, supply planning and supply chain management business environments. </font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">looking for contract SAP Trainer to work directly with associates in the customer service, supply planning and demand planning areas. </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Must have strong experience in SAP MM, SD and WM modules in customer service, demand planning, supply planning and supply chain management business environments. Prefer experience in Wholesale Business Environment.</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 36.75pt; text-indent: -18.75pt"><font face="Calibri"><strong><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: red">2.</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 22pt; color: red">SAP PP-PI BA- #121401 &nbsp;(opened back up)</span></strong></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">St Louis, MO</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">7 month contract</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font face="Calibri"><span style="background: yellow">Face to Face &ndash; we do not pay for travel.</span></font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Will interview quickly for a strong candidate.</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Strong SAP PP-PI experience </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Strong SAP MM-PU experience </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">update from MGR:</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">The main reason for reopening was that the various candidates we received were either unavailable or seemed to be lacking in experience and exposure to both the PP and MM areas.&nbsp; As part of our interview process, we perform a hands-on exercise where the candidate must use SAP to do specific tasks.&nbsp; If the candidate is unable to navigate or perform some of the basic functions, they will not make the cut.</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">The general guidance is:&nbsp; Strong, hands on experience and ability to actually perform the work.</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Jennifer will be moving quickly and to review candidates on a daily basis.&nbsp; If we have a strong candidate submitted, she will likely be setting up face-to-face interviews quickly.&nbsp; Thus, it may be beneficial to prep candidates that a trip to St Louis could happen quickly.&nbsp; We encountered situations where we had to wait a week or more for candidates to be available for an interview.&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">The Manufacturing IT organization is looking for an experienced SAP PP-PI analyst that can perform business analyst and support duties.&nbsp; While SAP PP-PI is the primary role, significant preference will be given to candidates that also have strong experience in SAP MM-PU.&nbsp; Monsantos seed manufacturing business is complex and unlike typical manufacturing processes, therefore candidates must have strong technical experience and be able to quickly learn new processes in order to be successful in this role. </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">This person will be responsible for owning assigned tasks, identifying and resolving issues, assisting with compatibility testing, and defining/driving enhancements and configurations. </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Responsibilities will include: </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Researching, replicating, and resolving issues </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Configuring PP-PI to support plant production business activities</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Configuring MM-PU to support Grower Accounting and Payment activities</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Development of Functional Design Specifications and other detailed enhancement documentation to support custom program development. </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Cross-functional work with BI, QM, SCM, ABAP, FI, Basis, Operations, and other teams as necessary to resolve technical and process issues </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Working with users and IT team members to define and document business requirements, determine the appropriate SAP configuration/customization required, or to document why the requirement cannot be satisfied by an SAP-based solution. </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Skills: </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Strong SAP PP-PI experience </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Strong SAP MM-PU experience </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Experience with custom development solutions (ABAP)</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Ability to write technical specifications to give to developers </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Ability to work in a team environment </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Ability to work closely with Monsanto's business users </font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;Excellent verbal and written communication skills</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">The learning curve associated with the Seed Manufacturing and&nbsp; business process is steep, therefore the candidate must be technically strong.&nbsp; If they are trying to learn the technical while on the job, they won't be able to keep up and will wash out quickly.&nbsp; This role is to provide additional assistance to the existing team, supporting an existing implementation.</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">Submittal Guidance and Timing</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">No phone calls.&nbsp; I will only be looking at the candidates submitted through the system.&nbsp; I will be looking at skills and experience.&nbsp; Submit your candidate based on the market rate, not based on the recommended rate of the system.</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 36.75pt; text-indent: -18.75pt"><font face="Calibri"><strong><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: red">3.</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 22pt; color: red">SAP Basis Admin- Kuehl/Siegert- 8182 #121576</span></strong></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri">St Louis, MO</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri"><span style="color: #1f497d">12</span> month contract</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font face="Calibri"><span style="background: yellow">Face to Face &ndash; we do not pay for travel.</span></font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">12 month contract</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">SAP Basis Administrator </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">Responsible for the upgrade and maintenance of SAP based systems.&nbsp; </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">Responsibilities:</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Provide collaboration services to SAP based development and support teams.&nbsp; </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Analyze, develop and maintain data architectures and process models within SAP.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Perform SAP systems monitoring and performance tuning.&nbsp; </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Perform Oracle database backup and recovery administration. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Design and support interfaces between SAP Basis, NetWeaver and external systems. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maintain the SAP Data Dictionary and Oracle database objects. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Migrate SAP application programs and data dictionary objects into production. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Provide cutover implementation support. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BASIS configuration administration. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Provide 24x7 emergency SAP Basis support on a rotating schedule.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">Required Skills:</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3+ years SAP Basis Administration experience.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Knowledge in UNIX, Oracle, SQL and CRM systems architecture.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4+ years of experience in relational and/or hierarchical database technologies.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In-depth knowledge of data modeling concepts and client/server technology. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Broad knowledge of integrated application development methodology.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Effective English written and oral communication skills, excellent problem resolution skills, and must like working in a team environment.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">Desired Experience / Attributes: </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Knowledge in NETWEAVER and ABAP/Java stacks.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SAP performance monitoring experience using CCMS.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Backup and recovery using RMAN (Oracle Recovery Manager).</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SAP Solution Management.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SAP Enterprise Portal.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri"><span style="color: #1f497d">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BS in Information Systems.</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Calibri"><strong><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: navy">Thanks &amp; Regards&nbsp;</span></em></strong></font></div>
