            <strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: navy; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'">&nbsp;|</span><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: blue; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'">nasir.k</span></u></strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black; font-family: 'Calibri','sans-serif'"><a href="mailto:%7Cr@nleague.com" title="mailto:ray.king@league.com"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: blue; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'">@nleague.com</span></strong></a></span><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: blue; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'">|</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: navy; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></div>
